title: The Bald Strawberry Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Gluten free restaurant, casual and quaint. Has vegan Daiya cheese, sometimes vegan baked goods (call ahead), and the kitchen will modify items to suit requests. Small menu with salads, waffle pizzas, and waffle sandwiches--the waffle, which is vegan, is used like bread. Moved from 2011 Melbourne Ct.
